item.title: About Me
item.description: My name is Jared Rosario and I am a 21 year old that was born in San Jose, California. I’m passionate about coding and music. For most of my free time, I’m either coding exciting projects or scrolling through my music library to find the perfect track to fit my mood. I’ve been coding since my early years, and I’m always striving to be better. I love to learn new things and build things from scratch, and I’m always seeking out new opportunities to advance my skills.
